    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">故事始于灰鬃团在深夜遭遇宿敌黑熊的大规模突袭，经过一场惨烈的搏杀，他们或战死，或流散。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">克里夫幸免于难，他决心寻回幸存的战友，并重建昔日的一切。在这段危机四伏的旅途中，他将缔结盟约、遭遇未知险境，并逐步揭开神秘势力的面纱。克里夫最终意识到，一个空前的巨大威胁以及一段远超其想象的命运，正等待着他的到来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/f4948f1e6cdd84885a78cadd255588d8.poster.avif?t=1770115850\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/f4948f1e6cdd84885a78cadd255588d8.webm?t=1770115850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/f4948f1e6cdd84885a78cadd255588d8.mp4?t=1770115850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/e6bdb5b0c288d3bf86879cbc926372fe.avif?t=1770115850\" width=1560 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">繁忙又热闹的大都市、悠闲宁静的小村庄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">广阔的绿地平原和炽热的沙漠。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">被人们遗忘的遗迹与神殿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">欢迎来到充满无数惊奇与神秘的广阔开放世界 - 帕卫尔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在这里，可以尽情狩猎、采集、制作，以属于你的方式在世界中探索，踏上寻找隐藏之路的冒险旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">时而骑着马匹或狼驰骋大地，时而乘着巨龙翱翔天际，时而驾驭机械，自此展开寻找未知世界阿比斯的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/ec3280ee0f7b04bc5107757926567e9d.poster.avif?t=1770115850\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/ec3280ee0f7b04bc5107757926567e9d.webm?t=1770115850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/ec3280ee0f7b04bc5107757926567e9d.mp4?t=1770115850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/4854e07b4f8a3a02adec6a7c1022a6da.avif?t=1770115850\" width=1560 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在红色沙漠残酷的战场上，没有既定的答案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">获得剑、枪、弓等武器，并结合强力技能与属性效果，发挥更强大的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">每一次攻击、每一个动作，都可能改变命运。在快速而激烈的战斗中，开辟属于自己的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/39c88712b2df9428e6611bbcb2ff7068.poster.avif?t=1770115850\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/39c88712b2df9428e6611bbcb2ff7068.webm?t=1770115850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/39c88712b2df9428e6611bbcb2ff7068.mp4?t=1770115850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/64a56346fb3f588ed7948764e7d7da3d.avif?t=1770115850\" width=1560 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">从冷血的战士到恐怖的巨兽，在帕卫尔大陆，有无数对你穷追不舍的敌人与威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">从惊险刺激的1:1决斗，到大规模战争、迅速而混乱的肉搏战，击败阻拦你前进的所有敌人与BOSS。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/1eadbf017621994f2e8d3bdd6bcc0162.poster.avif?t=1770115850\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/1eadbf017621994f2e8d3bdd6bcc0162.webm?t=1770115850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/1eadbf017621994f2e8d3bdd6bcc0162.mp4?t=1770115850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321460/extras/a952a65e94af169364becf20ab1bb3ae.avif?t=1770115850\" width=1560 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">多方势力彼此保持着紧张关系并共存的帕卫尔大陆的佩伦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">克里夫的身边始终有翁卡、雅恩、奈拉等灰鬃团成员常伴左右。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">但是这一切，在黑熊的袭击下毁于一旦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在与黑熊的战斗中，灰熊团成员一个接一个牺牲。克里夫和灰鬃团成员在与黑熊首领摩尔迪的殊死战斗后，最终四散各地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">将伙伴们的名字刻在内心深处的克里夫，立誓要重建破碎的灰鬃，完成对黑熊的复仇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">然后，在这段旅程中，他不仅会遇上企图破坏大陆秩序的势力，还将面临前所未有的新任务。</p>",
